description: Take our quiz to see how much you remember about what has happened across the English Football League in 2024.
title: How well do you remember the EFL in 2024?
title_page: How well do you remember the EFL in 2024? - BBC Sport
maintext:
It has been another incident-filled year in the English Football League.
The managerial merry-go-round has spun as quickly as ever, there have been record transfers in League One, and supporters up and down the land have experienced their share of joy and despair.
But how much can you remember about what happened in the EFL in 2024?
Take our 20-question quiz and let us know how you get on using #bbcefl on X.
